item.title: Big fish...
item.description: Today is a monumental day! Last month I mounted a 7 & 1/2 foot Pacific Sailfish caught in Puerto Vallarta Mexico in my rec room, but I needed to touch up the dorsal fin (the only part of the fish that is made of wood because it canâ€™t be preserved). Well, I finally got around to putting the finishing touches on it tonight (the black dots)……..hooray! I think it looks great!
